    @Entity(value="oval.def.state")
public class StateType
extends DefinitionsComponent
    An OVAL State is a collection of one or more characteristics pertaining to a specific object type. The OVAL State is used by an OVAL Test to determine if a set of items identified on a system meet certain characteristics.
